title: MONDAY 3/29 - Trevor Lawrence draft day plans
itunes:title: MONDAY 3/29 - Trevor Lawrence draft day plans
description:
Desean Jackson now a member of the Rams, he talks about looking forward to hooking up with Matthew Stafford this season (0:47). Bucs GM Jason Licht (1:18) happy his team was able to retain a majority of it's free agents. Aaron Jones has some "unfinished business" in Green Bay (2:49). Plus, where will Trevor Lawrence be when they call his name on draft night? (3:16)
